===結構===
早期的足球是由18塊矩形不防水的[[皮革|皮革]]縫合而成，3塊一組合共6組，長短邊相連，結構類似現時的[[排球|排球]]及[[蓋爾式足球|蓋爾式足球]]用球，為[[立方五角十二面體|立方五角十二面體]]的{{link-en|球面多面體|spherical polyhedron}}狀<ref name="Paul Bourke 2017">{{Citation | url = http://paulbourke.net/geometry/spherical/ | title = Geometry of sports balls | chapter = § Volley ball (Gaelic football, Water polo, Netball) | publisher = Paul Bourke | date = January 2017 | author = Paul Bourke | access-date = 2019-10-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180727054109/http://paulbourke.net/geometry/spherical/ | archive-date = 2018-07-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="article karimi2015measurement">{{Cite journal
  |title=Measurement of the mechanical properties of the handball, volleyball, and basketball using DIC method: a combination of experimental, constitutive, and viscoelastic models
  |author=Karimi, Alireza and Kudo, Susumu and Razaghi, Reza and Navidbakhsh, Mahdi
  |journal=Sport Sciences for Health
  |volume=11
  |number=3
  |pages=295--303
  |year=2015
  |publisher=Springer}}</ref>，留有約15厘米開口紮結縫線供放入內胆及充氣。這種結構的足球現時仍在使用。

